Do you think that schools should use more technology to help students learn
Yes, I do think that schools should embrace technology into their teaching methods, especially in today's modern world. Children are growing up surrounded by digital devices and the internet. Initially, they are strongly affected by the vividness of images, videos on social media platforms. That's why I think schools should keep updated and incorporate more technology in classrooms. With the help of technological tools like mobile phones and tablets, the lessons will not likely be dull anymore, instead they would be more engaging and spark student's curiosity. To be specific, students can participate in educational games, and quizzes that help to enhance their cognitive abilities and encourage healthy competition.

